<h4 id="For-Ubuntu-based-deployments" style=""><span id="RKE2Control-planeDeployment-ForUbuntubaseddeployments"></span>For Ubuntu based deployments
 <i18n-message i18nkey="clipboard.copyLink.label" attribute="description">
